Phase 1a complete. Three commits land cleanly:

- `b9bd238` rewires `agent.registry.ts` through `src/agents/` only and adds the resolution test (criteria 2-4).
- `d250874` deletes `src/flavours/`, the two flavour modules, and ten flavour-importing tests; reworks `check.ts`/`create.ts`; removes `--flavour` from every command and adds the deprecation guard with a 48-test parameterised matrix; restores three test files as flavour-free versions to preserve unrelated coverage; cleans up docs (criteria 5-6, 9-22, 28-30).
- `8ee4bb5` bumps `package.json` to `0.8.0`, adds `engines`, the optional Playwright peer dep, `axe-core`/`wcag-contrast`, and drops the `dist/flavours` build step (criteria 7, 23-27).

