- `src/ui/color.ts` (new) — semantic role helper exposing `error / success / warning / info / hint / bold / dimInfo`, `stripAnsi`, `clearLineSequence`. Honors `NO_COLOR` and per-stream TTY state; output is byte-identical when colors are stripped.
